<!-- END section -->
<section class="section blog-post-entry">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="heading" data-aos="fade-up">Consultation Services</h2>
                <p data-aos="fade-up">Choose the consultation type that suits your needs and preferences. Our virtual, and in-person consultations offer personalized and professional advice on fashion, style, and wardrobe, tailored to your lifestyle and goals.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <a href="#" class="mb-4 d-block"><img src="/images/in_person.jpg" alt="Image placeholder" class="img-fluid"></a>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">In-Person Consultation</a></h2>
                        <p>This type of consultation is conducted face-to-face and allows for a more hands-on approach to styling. It's a great option for those who prefer a more personalized experience and the ability to try on different outfits and accessories. Services such as Personal Fashion Advice, Color Analysis, Wardrobe Assessment, and Style Makeover can be done in person.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <a href="#" class="mb-4 d-block"><img src="/images/virtual.jpg" alt="Image placeholder" class="img-fluid"></a>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">Virtual Consultation</a></h2>
                        <p>This type of consultation is conducted remotely, usually through video chat or phone call. It's a great option for those who are unable to meet in person or prefer the convenience of receiving advice from the comfort of their own home. Services such as Personal Fashion Advice, Color Analysis, and Wardrobe Assessment can be done virtually.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="section blog-post-entry bg-light" id="next">
