                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <span class="meta-post">Men's casual and streetwear</span>
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">David Smith</a></h2>
                        <p>
                            Fashion graduate with 5 years of experience in styling men's fashion <br />
                            David is a trendsetter in the world of men's fashion. With his keen eye for detail and passion for streetwear, he helps his clients achieve a cool and effortless look. His laid-back yet stylish approach to fashion has earned him a loyal following of fashion-conscious men seeking a fresh and modern wardrobe.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <span class="meta-post">Sustainable and ethical fashion</span>
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">Emily Thompson</a></h2>
                        <p>
                            Certified sustainable fashion consultant with a background in fashion sustainability and eco-friendly practices <br />
                            Emily is a dedicated advocate of sustainable and ethical fashion. She believes that fashion can be both stylish and responsible. With her expertise in sustainable fashion practices, she helps her clients make eco-friendly choices in their wardrobe while looking chic and conscious of the environment.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <span class="meta-post"> Asian fashion and cultural fusion</span>
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">Sofia Chen</a></h2>
                        <p>
                            Fashion influencer and blogger with a focus on Asian fashion and fusion styles <br />
                            Sophia is a fashion enthusiast with a passion for Asian fashion and cultural fusion. She is known for her unique and creative styling, blending traditional Asian elements with contemporary fashion trends. Her fashion-forward approach and expertise in Asian fashion make her a go-to stylist for clients looking to infuse cultural influences into their wardrobe.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <span class="meta-post">Men's formal wear and business attire</span>
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">Carlos Rodriguez</a></h2>
                        <p>
                            Former fashion buyer for luxury menswear brands with 8 years of styling experience <br />
                            Carlos is a seasoned stylist with a wealth of experience in men's formal wear and business attire. He has an in-depth understanding of fabrics, cuts, and fits, and knows how to create sophisticated and polished looks for any professional setting.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 post mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <div class="media media-custom d-block mb-4 h-100">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <span class="meta-post">Boho-chic and bohemian fashion</span>
                        <h2 class="mt-0 mb-3"><a href="#">Gabrielle Martinez</a></h2>
                        <p>
                            Fashion blogger and influencer with a focus on boho-chic styles <br />
                            Gabrielle is a fashion blogger and influencer known for her love for boho-chic and bohemian fashion. She has a keen eye for eclectic prints, flowing fabrics, and unique accessories that capture the free-spirited and laid-back essence of boho fashion.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="heading" data-aos="fade-up">Choose the package that's right for you.</h2>
                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Our packages are designed to fit your unique style and needs. Whether you're looking for personalized wardrobe recommendations, in-depth fashion advice, or a complete style makeover, we have a package that's perfect for you. Check out our packages and see which one is the best fit for your fashion journey.</p>
